4 HR____ COMMENDING RICKY DAN HARCROW ON HIS RETRIEMENT FROM
5 THE DEKALB COUNTY COMMISSION.
6
7 WHEREAS, Ricky Dan Harcrow, of DeKalb County,
8 Alabama, is hereby commended for his many years of dedicated
9 service to the people of DeKalb County; and
10 WHEREAS, Ricky Dan Harcrow has rendered distinguished
11 and faithful service to the residents of DeKalb County,
12 through decades of committed public leadership, culminating
13 in his retirement from the DeKalb County Commission; and
14 WHEREAS, born on January 28, 1951, to Jack and Zelma
15 Harcrow, he developed a lifelong dedication to service,
16 integrity, and community involvement that would define both
17 his public and private life; and
18 WHEREAS, Mr. Harcrow began his public service career
19 in local government as a member of the Ider City Council
20 from 1984 to 1986, and subsequently served as Mayor of Ider
21 beginning in 1986; and
22 WHEREAS, in November 1998, Mr. Harcrow was elected to
23 serve as a DeKalb County Commissioner; in November 2010, he
24 was elected President of the DeKalb County Commission, a
25 role he fulfilled with distinction for 16 years; and
26 WHEREAS, his influence extended beyond county borders
27 when he served as President of the Alabama County
28 Commissioners Association, further reflecting his statewide
Page 1

Commissioners Association, further reflecting his statewide
HR23 INTRODUCED
29 leadership and dedication to strengthening county government
30 throughout Alabama; and
31 WHEREAS, in addition to his elected service, Mr.
32 Harcrow has contributed meaningfully to the economic and
33 civic development of DeKalb County through roles such as
34 Director of Tourism and through service on numerous local
35 and state boards; and
36 WHEREAS, throughout his career, Ricky Dan Harcrow has
37 been recognized as a man of integrity, diligence, and
38 humility, whose leadership has positively impacted the lives
39 of countless residents and whose legacy of service will
40 endure in DeKalb County for generations to come; now
41 therefore,
42 BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES OF THE
43 LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA, That we highly commend Ricky Dan
44 Harcrow for his many years of public service, and this
45 resolution hereby serves as a tribute to him with utmost
46 gratitude and admiration, along with sincere best wishes for
47 continued success in all future endeavors.
